Package: leri
Title: Access Landscape Evaporative Response Index (LERI) Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Max",
           family = "Joseph",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "maxwell.b.joseph@colorado.edu")
Description: Easily access and work with Landscape Evaporative Response Index 
  (LERI) data from R. This package provides utilities for downloading LERI data 
  and reading it using the raster package. More info on LERI is 
  avaiable at <https://www.esrl.noaa.gov/psd/leri/>.
URL: https://github.com/earthlab/leri
BugReports: https://github.com/earthlab/leri/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    rappdirs,
    raster
Suggests: 
    testthat
